Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.38,0:22:24.97,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}君の横顔が見詰めているのは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.31,0:22:28.63,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}次の季節だっと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.25,0:22:33.01,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}分かってるから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.21,0:22:36.26,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}痛いくらいに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.56,0:22:41.15,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}反射的に笑顔を作る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.59,0:22:48.25,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}曖昧な線　揺曳な隙まで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.50,0:22:54.66,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}無邪気なあざとさで夢を繋いだの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.30,0:22:58.06,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}噓だらけで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.30,0:23:00.95,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}傷だらけで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.22,0:23:06.07,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}純度だけは固くて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.19,0:23:10.07,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}ほら　眩しすぎて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.26,0:23:12.32,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}涙　ダイヤモンド
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.37,0:23:17.96,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}きっと終わりが始まってる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.36,0:23:24.91,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}ずっと忘れない季節でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.38,0:22:24.97,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}我凝视着你的侧颜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.31,0:22:28.63,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}是因为我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.25,0:22:33.01,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}那是下一个季节
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.21,0:22:36.26,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}反射般的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.56,0:22:41.15,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}我作出让自己心痛的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.59,0:22:48.25,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}暧昧的线在摇荡的缝隙间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.50,0:22:54.66,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}我用天真的小聪明延续着梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.30,0:22:58.06,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}尽是谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.30,0:23:00.95,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}尽是伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.22,0:23:06.07,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}唯有纯度坚固如昔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.19,0:23:10.07,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}看 那耀眼的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.26,0:23:12.32,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}泪水的钻石
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.37,0:23:17.96,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HFF0000&}结局一定开始了吧
